  <brief_title>Efficacy of Metacognitive Training Single Modules: Jumping to Conclusions and To Empathize...</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Metacognitive Training Single Modules: Jumping to Conclusions and To Empathize... Among Patients of Psychiatric Rehabilitation Ward With Diagnosis of Schizophrenia.</official_title>
